<div class="row" style="padding: 5px;">
	<div class="col-md-7">
		<h2 class="featurette-heading">About Church Finder</h2>
		<p class="lead">Church Finder is a website created by a group of university students who want to help people find churches with in the north island or New Zealand. Whether you're a visitor, a newcomer, or a long-time resident, our website can help you discover churches in your area. We know that finding a church that fits your spiritual needs and preferences can be challenging, and that's why we created this website.</p>
		<p class="lead">Our team members come from different backgrounds and denominations, but we share a common passion for helping others. We believe that churches are an essential part of the community, and we want to make it easier for people to connect with them.</p>
	</div>
