		<h2 class="featurette-heading">How to Use Our Website</h2>
		<p class="lead">Our website is easy to navigate and search for churches in New Zealand. Users can easily search for churches based on their denomination, location, or other criteria. We also provide a map for users to view the locations of churches around New Zealand.</p>
	</div>
