			<li class="list-group-item text-white" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%;">To provide accurate and up-to-date information on churches in New Zealand</li>
			<li class="list-group-item text-white" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%;">To make it easy for people to search for churches based on location, denomination, and other criteria</li>
			<li class="list-group-item text-white" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%;">To promote diversity and inclusivity by featuring churches from different denominations and cultures</li>
